    "description": "Swing over spikes and pits, find the secrets of a mysterious tree and overcome difficult challenges as a brave tiny lizard in this small adventure.<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755280/extras/649c660ae0ad993fb6121169ab816d37.avif?t=1639651395\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br>Super Grappling Gecko is an exploration game where you need to help a brave tiny lizard to succeed in his adventure with nothing but a hook. In this <strong>small adventure</strong>, you'll find challenging areas and dangerous enemies. Grab your hook and enjoy this adventure! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755280/extras/3bb2b9931b709e1afacf5e04cf0eff1a.poster.avif?t=1639651395\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755280/extras/3bb2b9931b709e1afacf5e04cf0eff1a.webm?t=1639651395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755280/extras/3bb2b9931b709e1afacf5e04cf0eff1a.mp4?t=1639651395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755280/extras/8e61168ae03fef4ff65683cac5600339.avif?t=1639651395\" width=616 height=100 /></span> <br><br>Features<br>- Classic Grappling Hook system.<br>- Explore a challenging world with hidden places. <br>- Short gameplay.<br>- 2D frame-by-frame animation.<br>- Speedrun friendly.<br>- Challenging Achievements.<br><br>What Super Grappling Gecko does not offer<br>- Combat system<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755280/extras/0f187219477f9a86bac126427cf38b43.avif?t=1639651395\" width=606 height=126 /></span> <br>Super Grappling Gecko is a metroidvania <strong>focused on exploration</strong>. Some other traits of this game: beautiful pixel art, original soundtrack, and skill challenger. It's perfect for players who like wholesome games and for players who enjoy speedrun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1755280/extras/a3aae655ca2a777d95c8258ad3080311.avif?t=1639651395\" width=616 height=100 /></span> <br><br>Super Grappling Gecko was developed by 7 game developers from Brazil. Together they have founded Calangames and want to develop many more small, unique, and fun indie games in the future.<br><br>We love to hear feedback from the community, so feel free to contact us! We will do our best to respond to messages quickly and fix any problems that may arise. 😃",
